formulas.name: Owner401kOpsTransferType
formulas.expression: CASE({!$Record.Termination_Transfer_Type__c}, "Termination","00G70000001hHu5EAE", /* HRS 4S Cancellations */ "Transfer","00G70000001hHu5EAE", "POP Termination","00G4u000004ogxsEAA", "FSA/HSA Termination","00G4u000004ogxsEAA", "NSF","00G70000001hHu5EAE", "QDRO","00G70000001RPj1EAG", /* HRS 4S LDPS */ "Death Distribution","00G70000001RPj1EAG", {!$Record.OwnerId})

formulas.name: Subject401kOpsTransferType
formulas.expression: CASE({!$Record.Termination_Transfer_Type__c}, "Termination", "401k Plan Termination", "Transfer","401k Plan Transfer", "FSA Termination","FSA Plan Termination", "POP Termination","POP Plan Termination", "FSA/HSA Termination","FSA Plan Termination", TEXT({!$Record.Termination_Transfer_Type__c}))

formulas.name: SubjectBySupportType
formulas.expression: Case ({!$Record.Termination_Transfer_Type__c} ,"Manual Trade – Distribution","3 day CAM case – distribution request" ,"Manual Trade – Distribution Correction","CAM case – distribution correction request" ,"Manual Trade – Loan Processing","CAM case – loan processing request" ,"FSA/HSA Termination","FSA Plan Termination" ,{!$Record.Subject})
